<H1>Copying directories</H1>

<P>To copy a directory use the command:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>cp -r <EM>directory1 directory2</EM></STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This copies <EM>directory1</EM> and everything
that it contains to <EM>directory2</EM>. The directory is created if it does
not exist.</P>

<P>If <EM>directory2</EM> does exist then <EM>directory1</EM>
is created as a subdirectory within it.</P>

